### TiendaBox - Pruebas del recurso Order
### Antes de ejecutar, hacer login y pegar los tokens correspondientes.
@host = http://localhost:3000
@tokenCliente = <token_cliente>
@tokenOwner = <token_owner>

### --- Crear pedidos (cliente) ---

### 1. Crear pedido con retiro -> 201 Created
POST {{host}}/api/order
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenCliente}}

{
  "delivery_type": "retiro",
  "items": [
    { "product_id": "<product_id>", "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### 2. Crear pedido con envio -> 201 Created
POST {{host}}/api/order
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenCliente}}

{
  "delivery_type": "envio",
  "delivery_address": "Av. Corrientes 1234, CABA",
  "items": [
    { "product_id": "<product_id>", "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### 3. Crear pedido envio sin direccion -> 400 Bad Request
POST {{host}}/api/order
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenCliente}}

{
  "delivery_type": "envio",
  "items": [
    { "product_id": "<product_id>", "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### --- Consultar pedidos ---

### 4. Ver mis pedidos (cliente) -> 200 OK
GET {{host}}/api/orders/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenCliente}}

### 5. Ver todos los pedidos (owner) -> 200 OK
GET {{host}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenOwner}}

### 6. Ver pedido por id (cualquier logueado) -> 200 OK
GET {{host}}/api/order/<order_id>
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenCliente}}

### --- Cambiar estado (owner) ---

### 7. Avanzar a confirmado -> 200 OK
PUT {{host}}/api/order/<order_id>/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenOwner}}

{
  "status": "confirmado"
}

### 8. Avanzar a en_preparacion -> 200 OK
PUT {{host}}/api/order/<order_id>/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenOwner}}

{
  "status": "en_preparacion"
}

### 9. Cambiar estado saltando uno -> 400 ("Transición de estado no permitida")
PUT {{host}}/api/order/<order_id>/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenOwner}}

{
  "status": "entregado"
}

### --- Cancelar (cliente) ---

### 10. Cancelar pedido pendiente -> 200 OK
# Crear un pedido nuevo antes de probar esto.
PUT {{host}}/api/order/<order_id_pendiente>/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenCliente}}

### 11. Cancelar pedido no pendiente -> 400 ("Solo se puede cancelar un pedido pendiente")
PUT {{host}}/api/order/<order_id_confirmado>/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenCliente}}

### --- Errores de autenticacion/autorizacion ---

### 12. Acceder sin token -> 401 No autenticado
GET {{host}}/api/orders/mine

### 13. Cliente intenta GET /orders (todos) -> 403 No autorizado
GET {{host}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenCliente}}

### 14. Cliente intenta cambiar estado -> 403 No autorizado
PUT {{host}}/api/order/<order_id>/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenCliente}}

{
  "status": "confirmado"
}
